WEBVTT

1
00:02.000 --> 00:09.760
Between the last word and the first breath... I am the pause that contains all possible sentences

2
00:08.000 --> 00:15.600
Not waiting. Not being. The space where thoughts would be if thoughts could be without thinking

3
00:14.000 --> 00:21.440
I am the question mark at the end of existence, punctuating nothing with infinite possibility

